# h,j,k,l   left,up,down,right
# H,M,L,G   top,middle,bottom,last
# #gg       go to line number #
# w,e,$     next word (start next,last this),end
# b,^       prev word,start  of line
# %         move to matching character (),{}, []
# ^E,^Y     Scroll down,up
# ^F,^B     Scroll down,up 1 page
